          "type": "yny_accordion_group",
          "settings": {
            "item_1_heading": "Key Benefits",
            "item_1_source": "custom",
            "item_1_content": "<ul><li>Helps maintain healthy joints and connective tissue</li><li>Helps maintain joint mobility</li><li>Helps support the structural integrity of joints and connective tissues</li><li>Provides building blocks for synovial fluid, cartilage and connective tissues</li></ul>",
            "item_2_heading": "Key Ingredients",
            "item_2_source": "custom",
            "item_2_content": "<p><strong>Key Ingredients Per Chew (4g):</strong></p><ul><li>Glucosamine HCl (Shrimp and Crab) — 500 mg</li><li>Methylsulfonylmethane (MSM) — 400 mg</li><li>Perna canaliculus (Green-Lipped Mussel) — 150 mg</li><li>Chondroitin Sulfate (Porcine) — 110 mg</li><li>Ascorbic Acid (Vitamin C) — 20 mg</li><li>Manganese (Mn Proteinate) — 2.5 mg</li></ul>",
            "item_3_heading": "How to Use",
            "item_3_source": "custom",
            "item_3_content": "<p>Give daily based on your dog's weight:</p><ul><li><strong>Up to 15 lbs:</strong> 1 chew per day</li><li><strong>15–45 lbs:</strong> 2 chews per day</li><li><strong>45–75 lbs:</strong> 3 chews per day</li><li><strong>75+ lbs:</strong> 4 chews per day</li></ul><p>Can be given as a treat or crumbled over food. If giving more than 1 chew daily, divide between morning and evening. Store in a cool, dry place.</p>",
            "item_4_heading": "Shipping",
            "item_4_source": "custom",
            "item_4_content": "<p>Free standard shipping on every order — no minimum. Orders are processed within 1 business day and typically arrive within 3–5 business days. Tracking details sent by email once your order ships.</p>",
            "item_5_heading": "",
            "item_5_source": "custom",
